        "subject": "LU-19242 tests: wait longer for recovery-small/26b",
        "message": "LU-19242 tests: wait longer for recovery-small/26b\n\nAdd an additional wait for recovery-small test_26b to see if this\nallows the test to pass, and how long it took.\n\nThis is not really a fix for the test, but it will avoid this issue\nfrom causing problems for other paches.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial testlist=recovery-small env=ONLY=26b,ONLY_REPEAT=100\nFixes: 0a5ee1a2a2 (\"LU-18878 ptlrpc: evictor/prolong timeout formula fix\")\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I93bf62e3ae25d0d28c218f8109170b28c260c731\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/61288\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
